<item>
            <title>[SPR-13059] MessagingMessageListenerAdapter should use DestinationResolver of MessageListenerContainer</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-13059</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using &lt;tt&gt;@JmsListener&lt;/tt&gt; and a &lt;tt&gt;@SendTo&lt;/tt&gt; the created &lt;tt&gt;MessagingMessageListenerAdapter&lt;/tt&gt; always uses a &lt;tt&gt;DynamicDestinationResolver&lt;/tt&gt;. When the used &lt;tt&gt;MessageListenerContainer&lt;/tt&gt; is configured with a different &lt;tt&gt;DestinationResolver&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is problematic in the case of using a &lt;tt&gt;JndiDestinationResolver&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A fix could be to set the appropriate &lt;tt&gt;DestinationResolver&lt;/tt&gt; in the &lt;tt&gt;setupMessageListener&lt;/tt&gt; method of the &lt;tt&gt;AbstractMessageListenerContainer&lt;/tt&gt; so that the appropriate one is used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
            <key id="63886">SPR-13059</key>
            <summary>MessagingMessageListenerAdapter should use DestinationResolver of MessageListenerContainer</summary>
