                            <comment id="116018" author="snicoll" created="Fri, 22 May 2015 05:52:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is actually already fixed on master for quite some time (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-12927&quot; title=&quot;MethodJmsListenerEndpoint does not set the DestinationResolver on the MessagingMessageListenerAdapter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-12927&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-12927&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Could you please try if that works out for you? I&apos;ll backport to 4.1.x when you confirm this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="116019" author="mdeinum" created="Fri, 22 May 2015 06:00:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank. Will do a test, I did a search before registering and didn&apos;t find this issue (wrong terms I guess &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; ). &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="116025" author="mdeinum" created="Fri, 22 May 2015 06:15:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Did a couple of tests and that indeed fixes the issue, a backport to 4.1.x would be great...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="116026" author="snicoll" created="Fri, 22 May 2015 06:37:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you so much for the quick reply. I am backporting this to 4.1 now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
